description: For sale: $365,000. Beautiful, custom built vacation home with 142 ft of lake shore on Wynne Lake! description: For sale: $324,500. Easy One Level Lake Living In This Well Kept Home W/Spacious Lakeside Yard & 3 Stall Garage! Set back off paved road on Embarrass Lake, just 17 mi to Virginia & only minutes from championship golf, skiing & dining at Giants Ridge. Easy access to area bike & snowmobile trails.  Built 1995, 2912 SF, 3+BR/3BTH, apx 1.3 acres & 162 ft lakeshore w/boat launch & sandy swimming. Full walk out basement w/high ceilings, bath, sauna, lakeside office, huge unfinished recroom w/glass French doors to open lakeside yard. Economical in flr heat. Roof & rain gutters only 8 yrs old, maint-free siding. New front, side & basement doors. Part of historic Voyageur's Highway, Embarrass is a 462 acre lake, 19ft deep & stocked w/walleye. Great move in ready home! Click link for 3D Tour!
